ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#56: FILE: drivers/char/istallion.c:795:
+		if ((brdp = stli_brds[j]) == NULL || (brdp->state & BST_PROBED))

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

